## Limitations
The report is based on available data up to October 2023, and some sources may have more recent updates that are not included. Additionally, while the consensus is strong, there are always ongoing studies that may provide new insights into the nuances of climate change and human impact. The report focuses on widely accepted scientific views and does not delve into less mainstream theories or opinions.